=== 评价 ===
在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]网站上根据267个专业评论有65%的好评度，平均得分6.6<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_an_unexpected_journey/ |title=The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |date=2012-07-29 |accessdate=2013-06-16 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422162003/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_an_unexpected_journey |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=The Hobbit: An Unxpected Journey Movie Reviews |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_an_unexpected_journey/ |work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Flixster|Flixster]] |accessdate=16 December 2012 |archive-date=2021-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422162003/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_hobbit_an_unexpected_journey |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上40家媒体的综评为58分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hobbit-an-unexpected-journey |title=The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey Reviews, Ratings, Credits, and More |publisher=Metacritic |date= |accessdate=2013-01-08 |archive-date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401004800/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-hobbit-an-unexpected-journey |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要的争议点是影片的长度和高帧數的拍摄技法，以及与[[魔戒电影三部曲|魔戒电影三部曲]]品质的比较；此外影片的视觉特效、配乐和演员表演都获得称赞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2243096/The-Hobbit-Early-reviews-An-Unexpected-Journey-good-great.html#axzz2KVkb5ZE2|title=Hobbit reviews good, not great|publisher=Daily Mail|accessdate=February 10, 2013|archive-date=2017-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121113951/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2243096/The-Hobbit-Early-reviews-An-Unexpected-Journey-good-great.html#axzz2KVkb5ZE2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2012/12/movie-review-the-hobbit-an-unexpected-journey-not-as-good-as-lord-of-the-rings/|title=The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey Reviews|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=February 10, 2013|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020074802/https://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2012/12/movie-review-the-hobbit-an-unexpected-journey-not-as-good-as-lord-of-the-rings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

